{"tid":1190320,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"認真一問 開風扇會冇咁熱定唔開風扇會冇咁熱","createTime":"2019-06-07T08:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T15:46:10.000Z","uid":237015,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"676fc31ec46dfe94fb5e159de80838552fae1418","tid":1190320,"uid":237015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"先講講背景(唔想睇嘅可以跳落下面睇問題) <br />\n話說我間房依幾日都係夜晚先開冷氣朝早醒就關咗佢 平時晏晝我就唔會喺房 房入面都冇開到窗<br />\n我老母依幾日就日日都幫我間房開風扇吹<br />\n話咁樣會涼啲 冇咁快變熱<br />\n但係基於我常識就覺得冇開風扇先唔會咁快熱<br />\n於是我就同佢嘈咗輪 我又唔識點樣解釋比佢聽我點解咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟啦<br />\n到底喺一個密封冇開窗門嘅房(初始温度係啱啱關冷氣嘅23度左右) 加上出面咁撚熱<br />\n1.開咗風扇先冇咁快變熱<br />\n2.唔開風扇先冇咁快變熱<br />\n邊個先啱<br />\n<br />\n以我直覺同常識諗就係2嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實際又係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f6939af87e1410866419771a1b327ebef3cf3ca7","tid":1190320,"uid":239033,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:28:23.000Z","msg":"日常生活 熱主要傳遞方法係互相接觸同輻射 <br />\n輻射就睇下個日天氣好唔好 無辨法控制 <br />\n另一個方法就係經過啲牆身傳熱<br />\n所以事實上係<br />\n<br />\n無錯!!! 係開唔開都無影響<br />\n<br />\n如果要再仔細啲講 開風扇會令多啲空氣接觸你身體 令冷氣快啲熱 但影響不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係想冷氣留耐啲 不如搵野封住個窗 會比較實際"},{"pid":"05ed622209b7421bf0373afd8f0c966525039cd6","tid":1190320,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"如果間房無人, 開風扇會快啲變熱<br />\n如果有人+風扇對住自己, 咁肯定係開風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657e527cafb32725810396174b2ceeca5fed0f0d","tid":1190320,"uid":237015,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"05ed622209b7421bf0373afd8f0c966525039cd6","tid":1190320,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"如果間房無人, 開風扇會快啲變熱<br />\n如果有人+風扇對住自己, 咁肯定係開風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"間房晏晝無人<br />\n可唔可以解釋下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想同老母解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a12a64b51ce3abc8f9b74c9322c1034483836a","tid":1190320,"uid":2450,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"657e527cafb32725810396174b2ceeca5fed0f0d","tid":1190320,"uid":237015,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"05ed622209b7421bf0373afd8f0c966525039cd6","tid":1190320,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"如果間房無人, 開風扇會快啲變熱<br />\n如果有人+風扇對住自己, 咁肯定係開風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"間房晏晝無人<br />\n可唔可以解釋下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想同老母解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHkWxRh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHkWxRh.png&h=0abcbb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開左風扇全間房一齊熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263300175b4374696f3c0f30213535bda8708df6","tid":1190320,"uid":237015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1a12a64b51ce3abc8f9b74c9322c1034483836a","tid":1190320,"uid":2450,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"657e527cafb32725810396174b2ceeca5fed0f0d","tid":1190320,"uid":237015,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"05ed622209b7421bf0373afd8f0c966525039cd6","tid":1190320,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"如果間房無人, 開風扇會快啲變熱<br />\n如果有人+風扇對住自己, 咁肯定係開風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"間房晏晝無人<br />\n可唔可以解釋下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想同老母解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHkWxRh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHkWxRh.png&h=0abcbb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開左風扇全間房一齊熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03be775fc24d8b02f5ea100739808e16314c7668","tid":1190320,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:47:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://science.howstuffworks.com/question22.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.howstuffworks.com%2Fquestion22.htm&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=2ca8fd8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.howstuffworks.com/question22.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5cdd742b244fe4addfbe6a3c82c92de330562c44","tid":1190320,"uid":136926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:04:26.000Z","msg":"應該係 2.唔開風扇先冇咁快變熱<br />\n因為空氣本身都幾隔熱，可以想像成房入面有一層層空氣，最外層嘅空氣最先變熱，之後變成一個隔熱層，減慢咗熱由出面傳入嚟咁。"},{"pid":"3fc89b1552c6e38de8a2d0dec299995c95b59582","tid":1190320,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"啲冷氣聚曬喺地下用唔到同熱咗無分別，如果風扇可以放地下吹返上頂，咁你用到冷氣嘅時間就會長咗"},{"pid":"8d227a15fb3757d396c7292eefb5e071d24dfb4b","tid":1190320,"uid":153136,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"如果好介意邊個對錯，最唔洗理論咪買個溫度計做實驗，計返幾次開同唔開嘅溫度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果講理論，我覺得就開風扇會熱d<br />\n因為空氣隔熱能力強，牆壁附近嘅空氣同牆壁差唔多熱，室內空氣就相對凍<br />\n開風扇令到相對凍嘅空氣同牆壁嘅空氣流動/交換<br />\n牆壁上嘅空氣同牆壁溫度差大咗，牆壁熱更易傳入室內"}]}